25:28.535 --> 25:30.935
Where are we at
with Jimmy Lincoln?

25:31.405 --> 25:34.039
Last known address.

25:34.041 --> 25:37.475
Thanks. Appreciate you sticking
your neck out for me, Harp.

25:39.579 --> 25:41.413
Her whole life
I've been watching her,

25:41.415 --> 25:43.782
and now here she is, and...

25:45.886 --> 25:47.819
