26:43.510 --> 26:46.044
This'll be a good spot
to hide out and lay low.

26:46.046 --> 26:47.812
This sucks.

26:47.814 --> 26:49.214
And when you wake up tomorrow,

26:49.216 --> 26:50.949
nothing about that
will have changed.

26:50.951 --> 26:52.951
Of course, you won't have
any bullet holes in you,

26:52.953 --> 26:55.620
so maybe it gets upgraded
to mildly crappy.

26:55.622 --> 27:00.558
<i>♪ I have made it
after a long ride ♪</i>

27:00.560 --> 27:03.428
<i>♪ Honey, now your sandman's
